	layer_6: my heart doth plead that thou in himdos lie a claset never pierced with christal eyes but the defendent doth that plea deny and says in him thy fair apparence lies
	layer_8: my heart doth plead that thou in hym dost lie a closet never pierced with crystal eyes but the defendant doth that plead deni and says in him thy fair apparence lies
	layer_10: my heart doth plead that thou in hym dost lie a closet never pierced with crystal eyes but the defendant doth that plead deny and says in him thy fair apparance lies
	layer_12: my heart doth plead that thou in hym dost lie a closet never pierced with crystal eyes but the defendant doth that plead deny and says in him thy fair apparance lies
